{"tid":1629160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(緊急)雲海話無保險賠單嘢,請大肆宣傳製造恐慌","createTime":"2019-10-06T07:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T18:24:50.000Z","uid":95520,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae7ccb935861e237ea757334d2c5d9721eafee1","tid":1629160,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:02:07.000Z","msg":"林鄭出得緊急法呢招就係想人同示威者割蓆<br />\n但賭注太大<br />\n<br />\n我哋要反其道而行大肆宣揚幫佢從中立撚同藍屍圈子入面製造恐慌<br />\n<br />\n呢單嘢已經唔會嚇到我哋黃絲<br />\n但藍絲呢邊咁支持緊急法就係覺得對佢哋完全無影響<br />\n嚇埋班藍絲同商戶<br />\n咁先可以最大限度咁比到壓力政府<br />\n仲有用過你成棟政總燒咗佢<br />\n<br />\n點解永遠只有政權可以製造恐慌?<br />\n政府比咗咁大張好牌你想你唔拉返啲敵人嚟自己陣營?"},{"pid":"edda927eb82c55642cef0417143c7e696949f882","tid":1629160,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c64376afb67645d910b009bdd9949b072d5ca1f0","tid":1629160,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ee508a6570e0c39279d3d28b816ac240a62f494","tid":1629160,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03a4555c8e333d06bcb06dc9b7179d305dcb6961","tid":1629160,"uid":6435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"加埋何妖自爆無保險公司受理果單"},{"pid":"de2d3fd91e58df272d04fe9da36937587666b94f","tid":1629160,"uid":155292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"可以從以下方向入手<br />\n話政府緊急法 為咗想幫保險公司減少賠償<br />\n官商勾結 好似Mpf咁"},{"pid":"cf1a4875ffb3e24f13ec4e56e594ea7bb980bb73","tid":1629